== 模板介紹 ==
{{Campaignbox 布匿戰爭}}
The various [[Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Military history#Navigation templates|navigation templates]] maintained by the Military history WikiProject are all intended to be implemented through a single base template, which combines the project's [[Template:WPMILHIST Infobox style|common template style]] with the [[Template:Navbox|standard navigation box format]].  This is needed primarily to allow multiple such templates to be stacked together—with each other, or with [[Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Military history#Infobox templates|infobox templates]]—to present the appearance of a continuous block; it is also beneficial for providing a consistent appearance to the entire set of articles within our scope.

== 參數及使用方法 ==
Any military-related navigational template should be created using the '''{{tl|military navigation}}''' base template, as shown below:

